{"tid":1872311,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企有個仆街細佬，就黎人都癲","createTime":"2020-02-10T04:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T10:10:11.000Z","uid":4187,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fceed439be24bf5afc77f8871d2f2373cba1481c","tid":1872311,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:28:07.000Z","msg":"我係大家姐，有兩個細佬<br />\n呀媽生完最細個細佬個陣難產死左<br />\n後來佢越大越最暴力，成日恐嚇話要上映六國大封相<br />\n所以Daddy都好唔中意佢...<br />\n後來舅父唔知咩事死左，我都凝住係佢搞出黎的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個細佬就死毒撚，成日玩公仔<br />\n好彩佢知自己樣衰，識遮住自己個死人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有次起身差D比佢嚇死，釘都飛埋出黎<br />\n<br />\n講返正題，Daddy撈開偏<br />\n有次想食大茶飯帶埋我地去開眼界<br />\n點知佢比人冼左一鑊，屋企得返我地3姊弟<br />\n有時諗起屋企兩個細佬，真係唔想返去<br />\n有冇人可以收留我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440195bc0c33bfd8ce38d8d8470896af73f748e6","tid":1872311,"uid":187987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"8ee34b91db3463f993dee1a258fd166406c71314","tid":1872311,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:30:47.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"3d84c796710eb734dd8a194a11742baa3298cd51","tid":1872311,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ee34b91db3463f993dee1a258fd166406c71314","tid":1872311,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:30:47.000Z","msg":"拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb7d2440bb702a60f3af799325b0cd1a9943902","tid":1872311,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c326247baad37d92c0920f1e5867b35387d1a83a","tid":1872311,"uid":301523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"